data.description: WOW! This charming home is located in a fantastic area of Clearwater, just 10 minutes to Downtown Clearwater, 20 minutes to Clearwater Beach, 10 minutes to quaint Dunedin, and 15 minutes to Honeymoon and Caladesi Islands! This home features a spacious open floorplan, and with over 1700 square feet of living space, there's plenty of room for the whole family! Inside, you'll find a bright, comfortable living room with access to the large kitchen - perfect for entertaining! The home has four bedrooms and two full bathrooms - one attached to the primary bedroom! Sleek tile floors with a wood-style finish adorn most living areas and add to this home's modern look.
